label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec916QLvCemVPgj2","target":"recy6BBIMIGwmihwL","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec916QLvCemVPgj2","target":"recbm5ZBUjTQ5uAGT","label":"mentions"}],"verses":[{"id":"recE1vjLLAgrziy6W","ref":"2Tim.3.1","text":"This know also, that in the last days perilous times shall come.","year":66},{"id":"recPCohgvFupaMo4m","ref":"2Tim.3.2","text":"For men shall be lovers of their own selves, covetous, boasters, proud, blasphemers, disobedient to parents, unthankful, unholy,","year":66},{"id":"recLSmCe34UaLs3KM","ref":"2Tim.3.3","text":"Without natural affection, trucebreakers, false accusers, incontinent, fierce, despisers of those that are good,","year":66},{"id":"rec38LybCLCxyhauA","ref":"2Tim.3.4","text":"Traitors, heady, highminded, lovers of pleasures more than lovers of God;","year":66},{"id":"recLUqujqUxM5RCvt","ref":"2Tim.3.5","text":"Having a form of godliness, but denying the power thereof: from such turn away.","year":66},{"id":"recM5Qxb2UVyfc3d7","ref":"2Tim.3.6","text":"For of this sort are they which creep into houses, and lead captive silly women laden with sins, led away with divers lusts,","year":66},{"id":"recVtVAhrcMtl3xGn","ref":"2Tim.3.7","text":"Ever learning, and never able to come to the knowledge of the truth.","year":66},{"id":"recFT6C6BhpvFj7mV","ref":"2Tim.3.8","text":"Now as Jannes and Jambres withstood Moses, so do these also resist the truth: men of corrupt minds, reprobate concerning the faith.","year":66}]}
